{"tid":567112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人李璨琛涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕 酒精濃度超標接近3倍","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T17:04:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b09d5bb5965a3d29d786fd671036121d3790383","tid":567112,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"藝人李璨琛（Sam）涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。消息稱，警方為打擊酒後駕駛，今晨在新蒲崗太子道東近油站設路障，隨機截查車輛。至早上7時48分，李駕駛其黑色平治駛經時遭交通警截查。他接受俗稱「吹波波」的酒精呼氣測試為86度，稍後返警署「吹大機」亦達到58度，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕，案件交由東九龍總區交通部跟進，李已經獲准保釋外出，三月下旬返警署報到。"},{"pid":"72edaede066400fe107df06e1f41d74701644631","tid":567112,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來仲有呢位明星？？？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c0e307c9af76807d42ce138ca6a86248aeedc8","tid":567112,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"瑞士山區肺"},{"pid":"f16f6471ce81679256129a3f791038637831117c","tid":567112,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca6a67f537eb22fb7f7801e5266ff590607e9a61","tid":567112,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"認真，邊個黎"},{"pid":"a87317d5963b818508af420802e246dcb0ca811c","tid":567112,"uid":10707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"老鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb5f4fc6c30359831164f4248760e390613f22f","tid":567112,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"未驗頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無抽血驗遮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h